headline: Paychex price target raised to $137 from $133 at Morgan Stanley
summary: Morgan Stanley raised the firm’s price target on Paychex (PAYX) to $137 from $133 and keeps an Equal Weight rating on the shares. Amid “a more conservative underwriting posture in the insurance agency” and events like hurricanes in Florida, Paychex “continues to execute well,” the analyst tells investors.
